title: Great Big Sea - XX (2CD Best of) - 2012 [flac]
description:
Great Big Sea - XX (2CD Best of) - 2012 [flac]

XX marks 20 years of Great Big Sea, the folk-rock band from Newfoundland, best known for performing energetic rock interpretations of traditional Newfoundland folk songs including sea shanties, which draw from the island's 500-year-old Irish, Scottish, and English heritage.
